  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "This model has been applied in clinical research settings to support ventricular assist device development. A CFD hemolysis prediction model for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump was evaluated under ventricular assist device conditions. The computational model predicts absolute hemolysis levels; Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed. All 13 credibility factors were assessed under ASME V&V 40-2018 at Model Risk Level 5. Seven factors were fully assessed; six factors were partially addressed. The overall credibility evidence is considered sufficient for the intended submission context, and the decision record reflects acceptance by the credibility assessment team. No structured Context of Use object is provided under the Minimal profile; the intended-use scope is conveyed through this narrative description alone.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5-requirement",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-hemolysis-cfd-credibility",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/cfd-hemolysis-fda-centrifugal-pump",
  "bindsDataset": [
