    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor gaps identified at MRL 5, the assessment team determined that the available evidence is sufficient for the intended regulatory submission context given the conservative safety margins applied in the device design. Six factors remain as epistemic gaps to be addressed in subsequent assessment cycles. The decision reflects acceptance conditional on the narrative scope described in this package; no formal Context of Use object is registered under the Minimal profile.",
